headline: Integrated Solutions Appoints Greg Arms to Board of Directors
summary: Integrated Solutions for Benefits and Insurance Services (IS Benefits), a provider of stop-loss underwriting, specialty drug management, and claims auditing for self-funded employers, and a portfolio company of Argosy Healthcare Partners (AHP), today announced the appointment of Greg Arms as a member of the Company's Board of Directors.

headline: Scott Gottlieb, M.D., Joins UnitedHealth Group Board of Directors
summary: November 18, 2025--Dr. Scott Gottlieb, former U.S. Food and Drug Administration (FDA) commissioner, is joining UnitedHealth Group’s (NYSE: UNH) Board of Directors, effective immediately.

headline: Is There Opportunity in UnitedHealth Group After a 36.5% Drop in 2025?
summary: Wondering if UnitedHealth Group could be a value play right now, or if the ship has already sailed? You are not alone, especially with so many investors watching for the next opportunity. The stock’s recent performance has been rocky, with a 10.1% decline over the past month and a 36.5% drop year-to-date. This has raised questions about both risk and reward potential from here. Health sector headlines have been front and center, particularly around rising costs and changes in government...
